QuestData.Title: Ears of the Lich King
QuestData.Description: Prince Keleseth acts as Arthas' eyes and ears in the Fjord.$B$BI don't like that one bit!$B$BGo and give him a round o' pain. You'll be doing the world a favor by doing so.
QuestData.LogDescription: Defender Mordun inside Utgarde Keep wants you to slay Prince Keleseth.
QuestData.CompletionText: It is good to see you again, $N.
QuestData.RewardText: I bet the pale whelp felt that!$B$BThat's one more step towards yer judgment day, Arthas!
